Here is a link to the Connectathon opening presentation..slide 10 lists what we have to report out on Friday. I will extract this slide and post it on Confluence and in Zulip (if I can): https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/14_6A6IGC8yLU1z_7qaLnnAdng7qU8XuzATyAQPXHXbQ/edit#slide=id.p10
